    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, garage-kept, and there\u2019s seriously not a single blemish on it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
