    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog performance. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is exceptional; the notorious rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The suspension retains its factory-correct geometry, ensuring the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering provides unfiltered feedback. Finished with original Style 67 forged wheels and a flawless interior, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the purist collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
